name: Virtual Network Service Coin
description: Virtual Network Service Coin (VNSCoin) is a BEP-20 token deployed on the Binance Smart Chain. It is designed to function as the native token for the VNS ecosystem, enabling staking mechanisms and facilitating decentralized transactions. VNSCoin’s smart contract is publicly verifiable on BscScan, displaying standard token behavior with no hidden fees, blacklisting functions, or tax mechanisms. The token is tradable on PancakeSwap, paired with USDT, offering liquidity and market transparency. VNSCoin’s structure ensures open auditability and straightforward integration with decentralized exchanges.
